he balmier months. Not only do they cover a multitude of sins, summer hair accessories allow you to experiment with style AND switch up your look in an instant.<br><br>From luxurious scrunchies to retro headscarves, we take a look the top summer hair accessories of 2021 that are gracing the hair of every trendy tressed influencer this season.<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-b796" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-jHkVzv kFoSDU pf-26_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-dVNjXY gaVfQc"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-27_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-28_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-29_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-31_">1.	Luxe Scrunchies&nbsp;</span></h2><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-32_"><iframe src="https://assets.pinterest.com/ext/embed.html?id=81768549476684395" height="618" width="345" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" ></iframe>

